  most accessible and versatile ways."""@en ;
  dcterms:modified "2026-06-07T15:30:29.324260Z"^^xsd:dateTime .

oakcurric:keylearningpoint-lesson-29452-1
  a curric:KeyLearningPoint ;
  rdfs:label """Textile inspiration can come from many sources and effective research helps develop
